143
00:09:39,762 --> 00:09:42,443
I mean story as an architectural construct.

144
00:09:43,384 --> 00:09:44,725
It's a set of consecutive moments

145
00:09:45,085 --> 00:09:47,666
that are imbued with meaning due to their context.

146
00:09:49,307 --> 00:09:50,968
While game mechanics are the building blocks

147
00:09:51,148 --> 00:09:52,289
of the gameplay experience,

148
00:09:53,029 --> 00:09:56,051
that is what the player does in the game,

149
00:09:57,051 --> 00:09:59,093
story is what emerges when you give

150
00:09:59,133 --> 00:10:01,174
these moment-to-moment experiences meaning

151
00:10:01,974 --> 00:10:04,896
by how you think about them, how you feel about them,

152
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:07,621
and how you talk about them with other people.

153
00:10:13,526 --> 00:10:14,988
But how you feel about your experience

154
00:10:15,728 --> 00:10:16,629
can be heavily determined

155
00:10:16,669 --> 00:10:18,451
by your sense of authorship over it.

156
00:10:19,652 --> 00:10:21,553
If I present to you a well-crafted story

157
00:10:21,573 --> 00:10:22,794
that you happily submit to,

158
00:10:24,616 --> 00:10:25,557
you'll come along for the ride

159
00:10:25,577 --> 00:10:27,158
and feel a strong sense of connection

160
00:10:27,699 --> 00:10:28,760
to what you have experienced.

161
00:10:29,891 --> 00:10:32,092
